The '''National Medal of Honor Museum''' is a proposed museum to be built in [[Mount Pleasant, South Carolina]]. It is slated for completion in 2021. Proposed by the '''National Medal of Honor Museum Foundation Board''', the museum is planned to be 140 feet tall, 20 feet taller than Mount Pleasant's next tallest building. The foundation was created in 2014 and aims to raise $100 million dollars to build the museum. Designed by [[Moshe Safdie]], the building has faced much regulatory scrutiny and criticism by the Mount Pleasant Planning Commission.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.postandcourier.com/business/medal-of-honor-museum-design-fails-to-impress-mount-pleasant/article_8f02f47c-3466-11e8-9591-fb912c11611d.html|title=Medal of Honor Museum design fails to impress Mount Pleasant council committee|last=Munday|first=Dave|date=|work=[[The Post and Courier]]|access-date=2018-04-05|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.moultrienews.com/news/medal-of-honor-museum-plan-to-come-back-for-approval/article_cd4ce9b0-1727-11e8-8a2a-4b15339f56d5.html|title=Medal of Honor Museum plan to come back for approval in May|last=Witte|first=Sully|date=|work=Moultrie News|access-date=2018-04-05|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/best-states/south-carolina/articles/2018-04-03/south-carolina-town-wants-changes-in-medal-of-honor-museum|title=South Carolina Town Wants Changes in Medal of Honor Museum|last=|first=|date=|work=[[U.S. News and World Report]]|access-date=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.charlestoncitypaper.com/CultureShock/archives/2018/03/27/with-final-design-for-patriots-point-medal-of-honor-museum-still-in-limbo-architect-speaks-at-charleston-museum-tomorrow|title=With final design in limbo, architect of Medal of Honor Museum speaks at Charleston Museum Wednesday|last=Hardaway|first=Connelly|work=Charleston City Paper|access-date=2018-04-05|language=en}}</ref> 

